        &lt;h3&gt;1. Install Docker&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-install-docker&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-install-docker&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Follow the official installation instructions to &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;install Docker Engine on Ubuntu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
